嫌洵堪認定。\r\n  ㈡核被告所為，係犯刑法第337條侵占遺失物罪嫌。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/CYDM/110%2c%e5%98%89%e7%b0%a1%2c1201%2c20220112%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"CYDM,110,嘉簡,1201,20220112,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"嘉簡","JNO":"1201","JDATE":"20220112","JTITLE":"侵占遺失物"}